{
  "texts": [
    "To address this challenge, we introduce a probabilistic pseudo-label dispatcher, which estimates a soft pseudo-label vector ξj i = { ξj i,k } for each instance based on the image-level annotation:ξj i,k = D α j i,k, t j i,k.",
    "(4)Here y i ∈ {0, 1} K is the image-level multi-hot ground-truth label.",
    "We set t i ≡ y i and denote its broadcast to instance j by t j i:= t i for all j ∈ {1,..., N i }.",
    "In other words, t j i is the per-instance copy of y i and the α j i,k denotes the learnable per-instance, per-class weight vector.",
    "We associate each instance x j i with a per-class confidence vector α j i."
  ]
}